model_query_pairs.query: Homepage hero banner — find practice name, tagline, and hero slideshow images ![hero](url)
Welcome paragraph introducing the practice, its philosophy, and what makes it special
3-4 key differentiators or reasons to choose this practice, each with a short description
Brief introduction for EACH doctor/orthodontist at the practice — include every doctor's name, credentials, and individual headshot photo ![doctor-name](url) for each
Overview grid of 3-4 main treatments offered (e.g., Invisalign, braces, retainers) with short descriptions and treatment images ![treatment](url)
3-5 patient testimonials with patient name, review text, and patient photos if available ![patient](url)
Social media links — find URLs for practice Facebook, Instagram, Yelp, Google, TikTok, Twitter, YouTube profiles
Schedule consultation CTA — find phone number, appointment request URL, and contact form link
About page hero with practice story headline and hero image ![about](url)
Practice mission statement or philosophy describing the team's approach to patient care
Full bio for EACH doctor/orthodontist — find all doctors, their education, credentials, certifications, specialties, personal interests, and individual headshot photos ![doctor-name](url) for each
Staff/team member profiles with names, roles, and team photos ![team](url)
Office tour photos — find all office images showing waiting area, treatment rooms, and equipment ![office](url)
Community involvement, charitable work, sponsorships, or local events the practice participates in
Schedule your first visit — find phone number, appointment URL, and contact form link
New patient welcome hero with encouraging headline and hero image ![getting-started](url)
What to expect at your first visit — consultation process, exam details, and what to bring
Payment options, insurance providers accepted, financing plans, and complimentary consultation offers
New patient forms — find downloadable PDF links, online form URLs, and health history paperwork links
Book your free consultation — find phone number, appointment request URL, and contact form link
Treatments page hero highlighting the range of orthodontic options and hero image ![treatments](url)
Early/interceptive orthodontic treatment for children — when to start, what it corrects, benefits, and treatment images ![early-treatment](url)
Adult orthodontic options — why it's never too late, discreet options, expected results, and images ![adult-treatment](url)
Traditional and ceramic braces — how they work, treatment timeline, what to expect, and braces images ![braces](url)
Invisalign clear aligners — how they work, who's a candidate, benefits, and Invisalign images ![invisalign](url)
Surgical orthodontics — when jaw surgery is needed, the process, and coordinated treatment approach
Retainers and post-treatment care — types of retainers, how long to wear them, and maintaining results
Advanced orthodontic technology — 3D scanning, digital X-rays, iTero scanner, and technology images ![technology](url)
Schedule a treatment consultation — find phone number, appointment URL, and contact form link
Contact page hero with welcoming message and contact image ![contact](url)
Office locations — find full address, phone number, fax, office hours for each location, and Google Maps link
Contact form — find appointment request form URL, contact form URL, and form field details
FAQ page hero introducing common patient questions
Common patient questions and answers about treatment options, insurance, appointments, and care instructions
Schedule a consultation — find phone number, appointment request URL, and contact form link
